Quel est la variation du Ca entre 2 mois consécutifs en 2025

-- Requête SQL envoyée :

WITH total_monthly_ca AS (
    SELECT 
        c.year AS year,
        c.month AS month,
        SUM(c.ca_recharges) AS total_ca_recharges,
        SUM(d.ca_data) AS total_ca_data
    FROM 
        reporting_ca_monthly AS c
    LEFT JOIN 
        reporting_ca_data_monthly AS d
    ON 
        c.year = d.year AND c.month = d.month
    WHERE 
        c.year = 2025
    GROUP BY 
        c.year, c.month
),
ca_variation AS (
    SELECT 
        year,
        month,
        (total_ca_recharges + total_ca_data) AS total_ca,
        LAG(total_ca_recharges + total_ca_data) OVER (ORDER BY year, month) AS prev_month_ca
    FROM 
        total_monthly_ca
)
SELECT 
    year,
    month,
    total_ca,
    prev_month_ca,
    (total_ca - prev_month_ca) AS ca_variation
FROM 
    ca_variation
ORDER BY 
    year, month;
